flowchart TD
    U1[Donor User] --> FE[Flask + Jinja UI]
    U2[Hospital User] --> FE
    U3[Admin User] --> FE

    FE --> API[Route Layer in main.py]
    API --> LOGIC[Business Logic in app/logic.py]
    LOGIC --> DB[(SQLite Database)]

    DB --> T1[Triggers\nSafety + Status + Audit]
    DB --> V1[Views\nInventory + Critical + Expiring]
    DB --> M1[Master Tables\nBlood Groups, Urgency, Status, Components]

    LOGIC --> A1[Smart Allocation Engine]
    LOGIC --> A2[Shortage Forecast Engine]
    LOGIC --> A3[Donor Loyalty Engine]

    A1 --> DB
    A2 --> DB
    A3 --> DB

    DB --> OUT1[Audit Trail]
    DB --> OUT2[Inventory Dashboards]
    DB --> OUT3[Fulfillment History]
